com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Models

Class Photograph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psychic_engine.cmput301w17t10.feelsappman.Models.Photograph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photograph
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The photograph model contain the bitmap used to display the images that the participant would like to add. The photograph will need to restricted to the uncompressed size of 65536 bytes. This enables the photograph to be stored in the elastic server and retrieved when needed.
